content: I'd like to wake up at 7:00 AM for work, but lately, I've been waking up around 7:30 AM. My current morning routine is supposed to include a 10-minute meditation session, but I've only been able to stick to it three times this week. I also have a cup of coffee and check my emails before heading out the door. It usually takes me about 45 minutes to get ready for work.
